metadata.name: Permissionless Fruit
metadata.description:
"Checks by Jack Butcher" has created a movement-- "An infinite canvas for expression designed to challenge the concept of ownership and authorship in the age of internet," as described by Jack. It has unleashed playful creativity. People have been having fun putting their own spin on it. And the bug has bit me as well. Have you been bitten yet?

Art-first-Art-only.
